text: Tampereen Pyrintö is a basketball team from Tampere, Finland. Pyrintö plays its home games at Pyynikin palloiluhalli. Pyrintö has won three Finnish championships (2010, 2011 and 2014) and two Finnish Cups (1969, 2013). == Other websites == * Official website * Pyrinto Tampere eurobasket.com Category:Basketball teams Category:Tampere Category:Sports organizations of Finland
